    dc:description "Figure 4. Phylogram of clade A.A, phylogram of clades A1–A4 from Figure 3. B, phylogram of clade A from Figure 3, except for clades A1–A4. C, phylogram of clade A from Figure 2." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7035978/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7035987>
    dc:description "Figure 7. Shell of Anomalodiscus squamosus (A–D) and Timoclea scarbra (E–H). A, E, external view of left valve and internal view of right valve. B, F, sculpture. C, G, hinge. D, H, fluted crenulations." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7035987/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7035985>
    dc:description "Figure 6. Gene arrangements of mitogenomes in venerids. A, gene arrangements in Venerinae, Chioninae, Dosiniinae and Gouldiinae. B, gene arrangements of species from different subfamilies sharing the same order of protein-coding genes." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7035985/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

